keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map R reload hard
map m Marks.activateCreateMode swap
map M Marks.activateGotoMode swap
map D duplicateTab
map ;b LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map d removeTab
map u restoreTab
map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
map , goPrevious
map . goNext
unmap <c-e>
unmap <c-y>
unmap zH
unmap zL
unmap i
unmap v
unmap V
unmap <a-f>
unmap [[
unmap ]]
unmap gf
unmap gF
unmap gt
unmap gT
unmap ^
unmap g0
unmap g$
unmap <a-p>
unmap <a-m>
unmap x
unmap X
unmap W
unmap <<
unmap >>
unmap gs
unmap yt
unmap Y
unmap `
nextPatterns: next,more,newer,>,›,→,»,≫,>>,下一页,下一頁,下一张,下一话,下一章
previousPatterns: prev,previous,back,older,<,‹,←,«,≪,<<,上一页,上一頁,上一张,上一话,上一章
